而且你不相信陌生人
and you don't trust strangers.

239
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:50,800
- 这不怪你 你不能相信这些人  - Jane
- And I don't blame you. You can't trust these guys.  - Jane.

240
00:10:50,800 --> 00:10:52,500
