I mean, they mean well,

241
00:10:52,500 --> 00:10:55,560
只要你配合他们 就会找到你丈夫的
and they'll find your husband if you let them do their thing.

242
00:10:55,560 --> 00:10:58,330
- 空口白话  - 信不信随你
