Why are you asking the FBI to meet your spiritual needs?

244
00:11:02,060 --> 00:11:03,930
你没有自己信任的灵媒吗?
Don't you have a trusted psychic of your own?

245
00:11:03,930 --> 00:11:06,060
有 他叫Cleo
I do. Cleo.

246
00:11:06,060 --> 00:11:08,130
