So that this city can pull together and help find him.

316
00:14:16,630 --> 00:14:18,630
这是你救丈夫性命
That is your only hope

317
00:14:18,630 --> 00:14:22,130
唯一的希望了
at saving your husband's life.

318
00:14:22,130 --> 00:14:23,300
好的
Okay.

