她去哪?
Where's she going?

321
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:34,130
她... 想给媒体打电话
She, uh... wants to call the press.

322
00:14:34,130 --> 00:14:35,830
我试图阻止她了
I... I... I tried to stop her.

