Downstairs.

324
00:14:41,330 --> 00:14:44,000
你真是很想被关回牢里啊
You must really miss that prison cell.

325
00:14:46,900 --> 00:14:48,430
我会试着跟她谈谈
I'll try and talk to her.

326
00:14:48,430 --> 00:14:50,530
你已经说得够多了
You have done enough talking.

327
00:14:56,060 --> 00:14:58,700
嗨
Hi.

328
00:15:33,330 --> 00:15:34,900
Jane回到屋顶后
After Jane returned to the roof,

