00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:34,330
你什么意思?
What do you mean?

354
00:16:34,330 --> 00:16:36,400
没我的事了 Jane逃走了
I have no business. Jane's gone.

355
00:16:36,400 --> 00:16:38,400
